text: When Moses returned his people angry disappointed he dictus Quod terrible thing vos habet perfecit in my absence! Could vos non wait commandments tuus Dominus? He threw down tablets took habuit de his frater head pulling eum towards ipse! (Aaron) dictus Filius my mater people took advantage de my marasmus fere killed me! Let non my enemies rejoice perfecit non comes me transgressing people
